>\n<td class=\"Horse_Info\">\n<dl class=\"fc\">\n<dt class=\"Horse\">\n<a href=\"https://db.netkeiba.com/horse/2023104738/\">\n\n ドウドウファイト<img id=\"myhorse_2023104738\" class=\"disp_none Favorite\" src=\"https://cdn.netkeiba.com/img.orepro//common/img/icon/icon_horse.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"18\">\n</a>\n</dt>\n<dd class=\"Age\">牡3</dd>\n<dd class=\"Jockey\">\n木幡初 57.0\n<!--01153-->\n</dd>\n\n</dl>\n</td>\n<td class=\"Popular\">\n\n<span>107.3</span>\n<br />\n<span>14人気</span>\n</td>\n\n<td class=\"Vote_Bar\">\n<div class=\"Vote_Bar_blue\" style=\"width:0%;\"></div>\n<span>6人</span>\n</td>\n</tr><tr class=\"HorseList \" id=\"tr_2\">\n<td id=\"act_waku_8\" class=\"Waku8\">14</td>\n<td class=\"Vote\">\n<ul class=\"\">\n<li class=\"Honmei\">\n<input type=\"radio\" id=\"m1-2\" name=\"\" value=\"1_2\">\n<label id=\"ml1-2\" for=\"m1-2\" class=\"\">&nbsp;</label>\n</li>\n<li class=\"Taiko\">\n<input type=\"radio\" id=\"m2-2\" name=\"\" value=\"2_2\">\n<label id=\"ml2-2\" for=\"m2-2\" class=\"\">&nbsp;</label>\n</li>\n<li class=\"Tanana\">\n<input type=\"radio\" id=\"m3-2\" name=\"\" value=\"3_2\">\n<label id=\"ml3-2\" for=\"m3-2\" class=\"\">&nbsp;</label>\n</li>\n<li class=\"Renka\">\n<input type=\"radio\" id=\"m4-2\" name=\"\" value=\"4_2\">\n<label id=\"ml4-2\" for=\"m4-2\" class=\"\">&nbsp;</label>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n<td class=\"Horse_Info\">\n<dl class=\"fc\">\n<dt class=\"Horse\">\n<a href=\"https://db.netkeiba.com/horse/2023106958/\">\n\n ガーディアンテイル<img id=\"myhorse_2023106958\" class=\"disp_none Favorite\" src=\"https://cdn.netkeiba.com/img.orepro//common/img/icon/icon_horse.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"18\">\n</a>\n</dt>\n<dd class=\"Age\">牡3</dd>\n<dd class=\"Jockey\">\n岩田康 57.0\n<!--05203-->\n</dd>\n\n</dl>\n</td>\n<td class=\"Popular\">\n<span class=\"Odds_Ninki\">5.1</span>\n\n<br />\n<span>3人気</span>\n</td>\n\n<td class=\"Vote_Bar\">\n<div class=\"Vote_Bar_blue\" style=\"width:10%;\"></div>\n<span>213人</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<!-- /.Shutuba_HorseList -->\n<div class=\"Yoso_Description\">\n<p>印の入力は◎だけ必須です。△は複数選択できます。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ModeToggleBlock\">\n<h2 class=\"Content_Title_Bar\">あなたの予想</h2>\n<div id=\"Kaime_Detail\">\n<div class=\"Kaime_Box\">\n<div class=\"BakenImage_Box fc\">\n<span id=\"baken_image\"></span>\n</div>\n<div id=\"view-kaime_open2\" class=\"ipat_menu fc\">\n<button id=\"act-ipat\" class=\"Common_Btn\">買い目を変更する</button>\n<span id=\"msg-ipat\" class=\"disp_none\">※買い目の入力・変更は枠順確定後から行うことができます。</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"Yoso_Text_List\">\n<div class=\"Tips_Toggle_Box\">\n<div class=\"Tips_Title\">\n買い目について\n</div>\n<div class=\"Tips_Body disp_none\">\n<p>入力した印の数で買い目が自動で入ります。</p>\n<p>印1個：単勝</p>\n<p>印2個：単勝、馬連</p>\n<p>印3&#xFF5E;8個：単勝、馬連BOX・3連複BOX</p>\n<p>印9&#xFF5E;13個：単勝、馬連流し・3連複流し</p>\n<p>印14個以上：単勝、馬連流し</p>\n<br />\n<p>「買い目を入力する・変更する」を選ぶと、買い目を自由に入力することができます。ただし一度変更すると、印による自動入力が解除されます。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"Kenkai\">\n<div class=\"YosokaKenkaiForm\">\n<textarea placeholder=\"あなたの見解を入力してください。（任意）\" name=\"act-comment\" id=\"act-comment\" onkeyup=\"resize_textarea(event)\" rows=\"1\"></textarea>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<a name=\"ipat_after\"></a>\n<div class=\"Bet_Btn_Box\">\n<div class=\"Special_Check\">\n<div class=\"ModeToggleBlock\">\n<input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"c-special\" name=\"\" value=\"1\" class=\"disp_none\"/>\n<label for=\"c-special\" class=\"Bet_On\">勝負レース</label>\n<p>払戻金2倍(1週1回まで)</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"Spesial_Fix\">\n<button id=\"act-bet_202606030302\">\n<img id=\"bet_button_add\" class=\"disp_none\" src=\"https://cdn.netkeiba.com/img.orepro//common/img/orepro/bet_add_btn.png\" alt=\"この予想で勝負！\">\n<img id=\"bet_button_update\" class=\"disp_none\" src=\"https://cdn.netkeiba.com/img.orepro//common/img/orepro/bet_add_btn.png\" alt=\"この予想で勝負！\">\n<img class=\"disp_none special_stamp\" src=\"https://cdn.netkeiba.com/img.orepro//common/img/orepro/icon_special_stamp.png\" alt=\"勝負！\" >\n</button>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"ModeToggleBlock\">\n<div class=\"Target_Set_Box\">\n<input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"c-recover\" name=\"\" value=\"1\" class=\"disp_none\"/>\n<label for=\"c-recover\">回収率ランキングの対象に含まない</label>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- 出馬表のミニバナー(当ファイルは消さないこと) -->\n<!--<a href=\"/bet/win5_king.html\" style=\"display:block;width: 375px;max-width:100%;margin:20px auto 10px;\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.netkeiba.com/img.orepro//common/img/event/win5_king/20025_A_720_complete.jpg\" alt=\"毎週5レースに◎をつけてWIN5キングとギフト券をGET!\"  style=\"width:100%;\">\n</a>-->\n<!-- 出馬表のミニバナー(当ファイルは消さないこと) -->\n<!--\n<a href=\"/bet/grade_king.html\" style=\"display:block;width: 375px;max-width:100%;margin:20px auto 10px;\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.netkeiba.com/img.orepro//common/img/event/grade_king/20026_A_720.jpg\" alt=\"指定レースに◎〇▲をつけて重賞キングとギフト券をGET!\"  style=\"width:100%;\">\n</a>\n-->\n<!--投票モード切替スイッチここから-->\n<div class=\"YosoMode_Switch fc disp_none\" id=\"orepro_setting\">\n<div class=\"Contents_Width\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<label>投票モード</label>\n</li>\n<li>\n<input id=\"simple_bet_on\" type=\"radio\" name=\"r-simple_bet\" value=\"on\">\n<label for=\"simple_bet_on\">簡単</label>\n</li>\n<li class=\"on\"><!-- class=\"on\" class=\"off\"で見た目切替 -->\n<label class=\"img_on\" for=\"simple_bet_on\"></label>\n<label class=\"img_off\" for=\"simple_bet_off\"></label>\n<div class=\"Switch_Img\">\n<span></span>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<input id=\"simple_bet_off\" type=\"radio\" name=\"r-simple_bet\" value=\"off\">\n<label for=\"simple_bet_off\">買い目</label>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!--投票モード切替スイッチここまで-->\n<div class=\"Yoso_Text_List\">\n<div class=\"Tips_Toggle_Box\">\n<div class=\"Tips_Title\">\n投票モードについて\n</div>\n<div class=\"Tips_Body disp_none\">\n<p>投票モードを「買い目」モードに切り替えると、俺プロをより楽しむことができる下記の機能が使えるようになります。</p>\n<p>・買い目や金額を細かく決めることができます</p>\n<p>・的中時に払戻金を2倍にできる「勝負レース」を週に1レースだけ設定することができます</p>\n<p>・自信のないレースを回収率ランキングの対象から外すことができます</p>\n<p>・レース情報で入力した印を俺プロに反映することができます</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"Yoso_Text_List\">\n<div class=\"Tips_Toggle_Box\">\n<div class=\"Tips_Title\">\n投票時間とオッズについて\n</div>\n<div class=\"Tips_Body disp_none\">\n<p>発走2分前までは、何度でも予想の投票をやり直せます。</p>\n<p>馬券発売開始前はみんなの本命馬から算出した想定オッズが表示されます。</p>\n<p>馬券発売開始後は中央競馬で発表しているオッズが表示されます。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"Regist_Pop\" class=\"Content_Box disp_none\">\n<span class=\"Frame_Top\"></span>\n<p>「俺プロ」を遊ぶには、アカウントが必要になります。</p>\n<div id=\"Regist_Close\">\n<a href=\"https://regist.netkeiba.com/account/?pid=login&rf=orepro&return_url=https%3A%2F%2Forepro.netkeiba.com%2Fbet%2Fshutuba.html%3Frace_id%3D202606030302%26mode%3Dinit\" class=\"Common_Btn\">ログインする</a>\n<a class=\"Common_Btn\" id=\"Regist_Action\">アカウントを作成する（無料）</a>\n</div>\n<a href=\"\" class=\"close\" onclick=\"regist_pop_close()\">閉じる</a>\n<span class=\"Frame_Bottom\"></span>\n</div>\n<script>\n$('.Tips_Toggle_Box .Tips_Title').on('click', function() {\n$(this).next('.Tips_Body').slideToggle('fast');\n$(this).toggleClass('Open');\n});\n</script>\n\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery-confirm/3.3.0/jquery-confirm.min.css\">\n<script src=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery-confirm/3.3.0/jquery-confirm.min.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"https://cdn.netkeiba.com/img.orepro//common/js/route.min.js\" type=\"text/javascript\"></script>\n\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\n\"use strict\"\n// $Id: shutuba.html 255 2017-07-15 15:55:55Z ysimizu $\nvar _action_api_url = 'https://orepro.netkeiba.com/api/api_post_social_cart.html';\njQuery.getScript(\"https://cdn.netkeiba.com/img.orepro//common/js/ndcommon.min.js?170714\", function(){\njQuery.getScript(\"https://cdn.netkeiba.com/img.orepro//bet/common/js/orepro_mybet.js?230909b\", function(){\njQuery.getScript(\"https://cdn.netkeiba.com/img.orepro//common/js/promise-6.1.0.min.js\", function(){\njQuery.getScript(\"https://cdn.netkeiba.com/img.orepro//common/js/axios.min.js?180202a\", function(){\njQuery.getScript(\"https://cdn.netkeiba.com/img.orepro//cart/common/js/cart_api.js?180919a\", function(){\njQuery.getScript(\"https://cdn.netkeiba.com/img.orepro//common/js/user_setting.js?181004a\", function(){\n$(function() {\nvar bet_flg = false;\nvar is_login = '1';\nvar is_member = '1';\nvar page_id = 'shutuba.html';\nvar race_id = '202606030302';\nvar week_id = '7';\nvar jyo_cd = '06';\nvar race_no = '2';\nvar race_state = '40';\nvar group_mark = 'oremark_202606030302'; // 俺プロの印を保持するセッション\nvar group_bet = 'orebet_202606030302'; // 買い目、コメント、勝負レースなどの保持するセッション\nvar group_shutuba_mark = 'horse_202606030302'; // 出馬表の印を保持するセッション\nvar cur_mark = {};\nvar url_bet = 'https://orepro.netkeiba.com/bet/api_post_mybet.html';\nvar url_bet_complete = 'bet_complete.html?race_id=202606030302';\nvar url_gen = 'https://orepro.netkeiba.com/bet/api_post_bet_generator.html';\nvar url_baken_image = 'https://orepro.netkeiba.com/bet/api_get_bet_view.html';\nvar url_ipat = 'https://orepro.netkeiba.com/ipat/ipat_dispatch.html?race_id=202606030302&race_date=20260404&return_url=%s';\nvar url_shutuba = location.href.replace(/(.*)\\/(.*?)$/, '$1') + '/shutuba.html?race_id=202606030302#ipat_after';\nvar url_cart = 'https://orepro.netkeiba.com/cart/';\nvar url_user_setting = 'https://cdn.netkeiba.com/img.orepro//mydata/api_post_user_setting.html';\nvar sess_bet = {};\nvar max_special = '1';\nvar max_mark_limit = 25; // 枠確定前につけられる印の個数の上限チェック\nvar url_user_setting = 'https://cdn.netkeiba.com/img.orepro//mydata/api_post_user_setting.html';\nvar query = route.query(); // URL parameter\nvar syusai = '10';\t// 海外対応\nvar location_url = '';\nvar force_disp_comment = '0'\nconsole.log('query: %O', query);\n// 出馬表画面表示直後の投票モード取得・切替ボタン反映\nif ( force_disp_comment == 1 ) {\n// 見解を強制表示(イベントLP用)\n$('input[name=\"r-simple_bet\"]').val(['off']);\n$('input[name=\"r-simple_bet\"]').parents().prev().addClass('off').removeClass('on');\nchange_simple_bet_mode( 'off', /* db save = */ false, /* scroll_top = */ false );\n}else if (is_login == '1' && is_member == '1') {\napi_user_setting(url_user_setting, 'get', null, function(data) {\nif ('OK' == data.status) {\nvar config = data.data;\nvar my_bet_mode = config['simple_bet'];// 'y'=有効 'n'=無効\nif( my_bet_mode == 'y' ){\n$('input[name=\"r-simple_bet\"]').val(['on']);\n$('input[name=\"r-simple_bet\"]').parents().next().addClass('on').removeClass('off');\nchange_simple_bet_mode( 'on', /* db save = */ false, /* scroll_top = */ false );\nconsole.log(\"[login and member]simple_bet_mode=on\");\nconsole.log(\"simple_bet_mode=on\");\n}else{\n$('input[name=\"r-simple_bet\"]').val(['off']);\n$('input[name=\"r-simple_bet\"]').parents().prev().addClass('off').removeClass('on');\nchange_simple_bet_mode( 'off', /* db save = */ false, /* scroll_top = */ false );\nconsole.log(\"[login and member]simple_bet_mode=off\");\n}\n$('#orepro_setting').removeClass('disp_none'); // radioの初期設定が完了してから表示更新\n}\n});\n}else{\n$('input[name=\"r-simple_bet\"]').val(['on']);\n$('input[name=\"r-simple_bet\"]').parents().next().addClass('on').removeClass('off');\nchange_simple_bet_mode( 'on', /* db save = */ false, /* scroll_top = */ false );\nconsole.log(\"[not login or not member]simple_bet_mode=on\");\n}\n// 海外競馬は、枠番なし(白)\nif('30' == syusai){\n$('[id^=\"act_waku_\"]').each(function(){\nvar waku = $(this).prop('id').replace(/act_waku_/,'');\nconsole.log('waku: ',waku);\n$(this).removeClass('Waku'+waku);\n$(this).addClass('Waku1');\n});\n}\n// 買い目を見るの閉開 (from)\nvar cur_mode = 'close';\nkaime_open(cur_mode);\n$(document).on('click', '#act-kaime_open', function() {\nif ('open' == cur_mode) {\nkaime_open('close');\n} else {\nkaime_open('open');\n}\n});\n// 買い目を見るの閉開 (to)\n// 初期表示の状態遷移\nvar cart_api = new NDCartApi(url_cart,'json');\nif(undefined !== location_url && '' != location_url){\nwindow.location.replace( location_url );\ninitital_view();\n} else if (undefined !== query['mode'] && 'init' == query['mode']) {\n// 初回アクセス(mode=init)\ndelete query['mode'];\nvar url = sprintf(\"%s?%s\", page_id, $.param(query));\nconsole.log('url: %s', url);\nwindow.history.pushState(null, null, url);\n// 投票を取得\nget_bet(url_bet, race_id, function(data) {\ninitital_view();\n});\n} else {\ninitital_view();\n}\n// 印の入力\n$('#shutuba_block').on('click', '[id^=\"m1-\"],[id^=\"m2-\"],[id^=\"m3-\"],[id^=\"m4-\"]', function() {\nvar id = $(this).prop('id').replace(/^m/, '');\nvar val = id.split('-');\nvar m = val[0];\nvar seq = val[1];\nconsole.log('id: %s mark: %s seq: %s', id, m, seq);\nvar mark_num = 0;\nfor (var key in cur_mark) {\nmark_num++;\n}\nvar cur_id = sprintf(\"%s-%s\", m, seq);\nif (cur_mark[cur_id]) {\nmark_num--;\n}\nconsole.log('mark_num: %s max_mark_limit: %s', mark_num, max_mark_limit);\nif (race_state < '40' && mark_num >= max_mark_limit) {\nAlertDialog('',\"\\n印は最大\" + max_mark_limit + \"個までです。\\n\");\nreturn false;\n}\nanimate_mark(seq, m);\nconsole.log('cur_mark: %O', cur_mark);\nvar bet_id = [];\nvar bet_num = [];\nvar bet_price = [];\nvar bet_cd = [];\nfor (var key in cur_mark) {\nvar val = key.split('-');\nbet_id.push(val[1]); // seq 出馬表通番\nbet_num.push(1);\nbet_price.push(0);\nbet_cd.push(sprintf(\"%s_%s\", '', val[0])); // mark\n}\nconsole.log('bet_id: %O bet_num: %O bet_price: %O bet_cd: %O', bet_id, bet_num, bet_price, bet_cd);\nif (bet_id.length < 1) {\ncart_api.clear_item(group_mark, function() {\nif ('1' == sess_bet['auto_bet']) {\n// 買い目自動作成=yes\nbet_generator(url_gen, race_id, function(data) {\nconsole.log('bet_generator data: %O', data);\nget_baken_image(url_baken_image, race_id, 'session', function(data) {\n$('#baken_image').html(data.data);\nkaime_open(cur_mode);\n});\n});\n} else {\nget_baken_image(url_baken_image, race_id, 'session', function(data) {\n$('#baken_image').html(data.data);\nkaime_open(cur_mode);\n});\n}\n});\n} else {\ncart_api.replace_item(group_mark, bet_id, bet_num, bet_price, bet_cd, function(data) {\nif ('1' == sess_bet['auto_bet']) {\n// 買い目自動作成=yes\nbet_generator(url_gen, race_id, function(data) {\nconsole.log('bet_generator data: %O', data);\nget_baken_image(url_baken_image, race_id, 'session', function(data) {\n$('#baken_image').html(data.data);\nkaime_open(cur_mode);\n});\n});\n} else {\nget_baken_image(url_baken_image, race_id, 'session', function(data) {\n$('#baken_image').html(data.data);\nkaime_open(cur_mode);\n});\n}\n});\n}\n});\n// 自分で買い目を修正する\nif (race_state >= '40') {\n$('#act-ipat').prop('disabled', '');\n$('#msg-ipat').addClass('disp_none');\n$(document).on('click', '#act-ipat', function() {\nif ('1' != is_login) {\n// netkeibaログイン前ならダイアログ表示\nregist_pop_open();\nreturn;\n}\nif( is_member != '1' ){\ndo_regist_member( function() {\nconsole.log('do_regist_member');\n});\n}\nvar url = sprintf(url_ipat, encodeURIComponent(url_shutuba));\nconsole.log('url: %s', url);\nvar id_none = $('#baken_image_none').prop('id');\nif (undefined === id_none) {\nConfirmDialog(\"確認\", \"<br/>新規で買い目を作成しますか？<br/>\", function(stat) {\nconsole.log('stat: %s', stat);\nif (stat) {\n// yes\ncart_api.add_item(group_bet, 'bet_list', 1, 0, null, function(data) {\nwindow.location.href = url;\n});\n} else {\n// no\nwindow.location.href = url;\n}\n});\n} else {\nwindow.location.href = url;\n}\n});\n} else {\n$('#act-ipat').prop('disabled', 'disabled');\n$('#msg-ipat').removeClass('disp_none');\n}\n// 予想印による買い目自動作成(設定変更)\n$(document).on('click', '#act-auto_bet', function() {\nvar c = $(this).prop('checked');\nif (true == c) {\nConfirmDialog(\"確認\", \"<br/><br/>現在の買い目が無効になり、自動で作成されます。<br/>よろしいですか？<br/><br/>\", function(stat) {\nconsole.log('stat: %s', stat);\nif (stat) {\nsess_bet['auto_bet'] = '1';\n// update session\ncart_api.add_item(group_bet, 'auto_bet', 1, 0, sess_bet['auto_bet'], function(data) {\nconsole.log('auto_bet: %s', sess_bet['auto_bet']);\n});\nbet_generator(url_gen, race_id, function(data) {\nconsole.log('bet_generator data: %O', data);\n// 馬券イメージ表示\nget_baken_image(url_baken_image, race_id, 'session', function(data) {\n$('#baken_image').html(data.data);\n});\n});\n} else {\n// checkboxを元に戻す\n$('#act-auto_bet').prop('checked', '');\n}\n});\n} else {\nsess_bet['auto_bet'] = '0';\n// update session\ncart_api.add_item(group_bet, 'auto_bet', 1, 0, sess_bet['auto_bet'], function(data) {\nconsole.log('auto_bet: %s', sess_bet['auto_bet']);\n});\n}\n});\n// 見解(コメント)\n$(document).on('focusout', '#act-comment', function() {\nvar comment = $(this).val();\nconsole.log('comment: %s, %s', comment.length, comment);\nif (comment.length >= 1200) {\nAlertDialog('',\"\\nコメントが長すぎます。\\n\");\nreturn false;\n}\nsess_bet['comment'] = comment;\ncart_api.add_item(group_bet, 'comment', 1, 0, sess_bet['comment'], function(data) {\nconsole.log('comment data: %O', data);\n});\n});\n// 勝負レースチェック\n$(document).on('click', '#c-special', function() {\nvar sp = $(this).prop('checked');\nsp = (true == sp) ? '1' : '0';\nsess_bet['special'] = sp;\ncart_api.add_item(group_bet, 'special', 1, 0, sess_bet['special'], function(data) {\nconsole.log('special data: %O', data);\n});\n});\n// 回収率ランキングに含まない(or 含む) 17.12.19\n$(document).on('click', '#c-recover', function() {\nvar recover = $(this).prop('checked');\nrecover = (true == recover) ? '0' : '1';\t// 逆なので注意\nsess_bet['recover'] = recover;\nconsole.log('recover: %s',sess_bet['recover']);\ncart_api.add_item(group_bet, 'recover', 1, 0, sess_bet['recover'], function(data) {\nconsole.log('recover data: %O', data);\n});\n});\n// 予想する\n$(document).on('click', '[id^=\"act-bet\"]', function() {\nif ('1' != is_login) {\n// netkeibaログイン前ならダイアログ表示\nregist_pop_open();\nreturn;\n}\nif( is_member != '1' ){\ndo_regist_member( function() {\nconsole.log('do_regist_member');\n});\n}\nif (false == check_mark()) {\nAlertDialog('',\"\\n投票できませんでした：印が不足しています。必ず◎は1つ入力するようにしてください。\\n\");\nreturn false;\n}\nif (true === bet_flg) {\nconsole.log('投票中');\nreturn false;\n}\n// 勝負レース指定の場合、既に使用済かをチェック\nif ('1' == sess_bet['special']) {\nget_bet_special(url_bet, race_id, function(data) {\nconsole.log('get_bet_special data: %O', data);\nif ('OK' == data.status) {\nvar sp_cnt = 0;\nfor (var key in data.data) {\nsp_cnt++;\n}\nconsole.log('spcecial count: %s', sp_cnt);\nif (sp_cnt >= max_special) {\nAlertDialog('',sprintf(\"\\n勝負レースの指定は同一週に%sつまでです。\\n\", max_special));\nreturn false;\n}\n}\nif ('1' == sess_bet['auto_bet']) {\n// 買い目自動作成=yes\nbet_flg = true;\nconsole.log('(1)');\nbet_generator(url_gen, race_id, function(data) {\nregist_bet(url_bet, race_id, function(data) {\nconsole.log('regist data: %O', data);\nwindow.setTimeout(function() {\nwindow.location.href = url_bet_complete;\n}, 500)\n});\n});\n}else{\nbet_flg = true;\nconsole.log('(2)');\nregist_bet(url_bet, race_id, function(data) {\nwindow.setTimeout(function() {\nwindow.location.href = url_bet_complete;\n}, 500)\n});\n}\n});\n} else {\nif ('1' == sess_bet['auto_bet']) {\n// 買い目自動作成=yes\nbet_flg = true;\nconsole.log('(3)');\nbet_generator(url_gen, race_id, function(data) {\nregist_bet(url_bet, race_id, function(data) {\nconsole.log('regist data: %O', data);\nwindow.setTimeout(function() {\nwindow.location.href = url_bet_complete;\n}, 500)\n});\n});\n}else{\nbet_flg = true;\nconsole.log('(4)');\nregist_bet(url_bet, race_id, function(data) {\nwindow.setTimeout(function() {\nwindow.location.href = url_bet_complete;\n}, 500)\n});\n}\n}\n});\n// レース情報出馬表から印を引用\n// ルール差異の調整\n// ◎◯▲は単一なので、最初のみ採用、☆(5),チェック(98),消(99)は反映しない\n$(document).on('click', '#act-mark_copy', function() {\nconsole.log('act-mark_copy');\n// 出馬表に存在する通番\nvar shutuba_seq = [];\n$('[id^=\"tr_\"]').each(function(){\nvar seq = $(this).prop('id').replace(/tr_/,'');\nshutuba_seq.push(seq);\n});\nconsole.log('shutuba_seq: %O',shutuba_seq);\nvar mark_mode =  getCookie('mark_mode');\nconsole.error('mark_mode: %s',mark_mode);\ncart_api.get_item_list(group_shutuba_mark, function(data) {\n// 一旦、出馬表の表示順に印をソート\n// 出走馬を柱にLoopし回避馬を除く\nvar ary_mark = [];\nfor(var i=0; i < shutuba_seq.length; i++){\nvar seq = shutuba_seq[i];\nif(undefined !== data.data[seq]){\nvar val = data.data[seq]['_cd'].split('_');\nvar m = val[1];\nif('check' == mark_mode){\n// チェックモード\n// '98' => △\nm = 4;\n}else{\n// 印モード\n// ☆(5),チェック(98),消(99)は除外\nif('5' == m || '98' == m || '99' == m)\tcontinue;\n}\nary_mark.push( seq + '_' + m );\n}\n}\nconsole.log('ary_mark: %O',ary_mark);\nif(ary_mark.length < 1){\nAlertDialog('','レース情報に有効な印が入力されていません。');\nreturn false;\n}\ninitial_animate_mark();\nvar ary_seq = [];\nvar ary_count = [];\nvar ary_money = [];\nvar ary_cd = [];\nvar m_chk = {1: false, 2: false, 3: false};\nfor(var i=0; i < ary_mark.length; i++){\nvar val = ary_mark[i].split('_');\nvar seq = val[0];\nvar m = val[1];\n//\t\t console.log('seq: %s m: %s',seq,m);\nif(m <= 3){\n// レース情報は、◎○▲などに数の制限がないので..\nif(true == m_chk[m])\tcontinue;\nm_chk[m] = true;\n}\n//\t\t console.log('m: %s',m);\nary_seq.push(seq);\nary_count.push(1);\nary_money.push(0);\nary_cd.push('_'+m);\nanimate_mark(seq, m);\n}\ncart_api.clear_item(group_mark, function() {\ncart_api.add_item(group_mark, ary_seq, ary_count, ary_money, ary_cd, function(data) {\nif ('1' == sess_bet['auto_bet']) {\nbet_generator(url_gen, race_id, function(data) {\nconsole.log('bet_generator data: %O', data);\n// 馬券イメージ表示\nget_baken_image(url_baken_image, race_id, 'session', function(data) {\n$('#baken_image').html(data.data);\nkaime_open(cur_mode);\nif('check' == mark_mode){\nAlertDialog('', 'レース情報の印を反映しました。<br/><br/>「チェック」を△に反映しました。');\n}else{\nAlertDialog('', 'レース情報の印を反映しました。<br/><br/>「☆」「消」「チェック」は除外されますのでご注意ください。');\n}\n});\n});\n} else {\n// 馬券イメージ表示\nget_baken_image(url_baken_image, race_id, 'session', function(data) {\n$('#baken_image').html(data.data);\nkaime_open(cur_mode);\nAlertDialog('', 'レース情報の印を反映しました');\n});\n}\n});\n});\n});\n});\n// 投票モード切替(簡単or買い目)\n$('input[name=\"r-simple_bet\"]').on('click', function() {\nvar val = $(this).val();\nvar db_save = false;\nif (is_login == '1' && is_member == '1') {\ndb_save = true;\n}else{\ndb_save = false;\n}\nconsole.log(\"db_save=\"+db_save);\nvar element = $(this); // ajax後はthisが変化\nif( val == 'on' ){\nelement.val(['on']);\nelement.parents().next().addClass('on').removeClass('off');\nchange_simple_bet_mode( 'on', db_save, /* scroll_top = */ true );\n}else{\nelement.val(['off']);\nelement.parents().prev().addClass('off').removeClass('on');\nchange_simple_bet_mode( 'off', db_save, /* scroll_top = */ true );\n}\n});\n$(document).on('click', '#clear_cart', function() {\nif (confirm(\"\\nセッション内容を削除します\\n\")) {\ncart_api.clear_item(null, function(data) {\nwindow.location.href = '';\n});\n}\n});\n//------------------------------------------------------------\nfunction initital_view() {\nconsole.log('initital_view');\n$('#all-page').removeClass('disp_none');\n// 投票状態セッションを取得\ncart_api.get_item_list(group_bet, function(data) {\nfor (var item_id in data.data) {\nsess_bet[item_id] = data.data[item_id]['_cd'];\n}\nconsole.log('sess_bet: %O', sess_bet);\nif ('add' == sess_bet['mode']) {\n// 買い目なし\n$('#act-ipat').text('買い目を入力する');\n$('#bet_button_update').addClass('disp_none');\n$('#bet_button_add').removeClass('disp_none');\n} else {\n// 既に買い目あり\n$('#act-ipat').text('買い目を変更する');\n$('#bet_button_update').removeClass('disp_none');\n$('#bet_button_add').addClass('disp_none');\n}\n// コメント\n$('#act-comment').val(sess_bet['comment']);\n// 勝負レース\nvar bet_special = ('1' == sess_bet['special']) ? true : false;\n$('#c-special').prop(\"checked\", bet_special);\n// ニックネーム\n$('#msg-nickname').text(sess_bet['nickname']);\n// 自動買い目作成\nif ('1' == sess_bet['auto_bet']) {\n$('#act-auto_bet').prop('checked', true);\n} else {\n$('#act-auto_bet').prop('checked', false);\n}\n// 回収率ランキングに含まない(or 含む)\nvar val = ('1' == sess_bet['recover']) ? false : true;\t// 逆なので注意\n$('#c-recover').prop(\"checked\", val);\n// 出馬表の印があるか？\ncart_api.get_item_list(group_mark, function(data) {\nconsole.log('mark: %O', data.data);\nfor (var seq in data.data) {\nvar m = data.data[seq]['_cd'];\nvar val = m.split(/_/);\n// レース情報、出馬表との互換性\n// 出馬表は、'馬番_印' 4:☆、98:チェックは△として扱う。99:消はスキップ\n// 0:-は削除\nif (val[1] == '0') {\ncart_api.remove_item(group_mark, seq, function(data) {\nconsole.log('remove_item data: %O', data);\n});\n} else {\nif (val[1] == '5' || val[1] == '98') {\nval[1] = 4;\n}\nanimate_mark(seq, val[1]);\n}\n}\n//\t\t     // 印→買い目の自動作成を行うか？\nif ('1' == sess_bet['auto_bet']) {\nbet_generator(url_gen, race_id, function(data) {\nconsole.log('bet_generator data: %O', data);\n// 馬券イメージ表示\nget_baken_image(url_baken_image, race_id, 'session', function(data) {\n$('#baken_image').html(data.data);\nkaime_open(cur_mode);\n});\n});\n} else {\n// 馬券イメージ表示\nget_baken_image(url_baken_image, race_id, 'session', function(data) {\n$('#baken_image').html(data.data);\nkaime_open(cur_mode);\n});\n}\n});\n});\n}\n//------------------------------------------------------------\nfunction kaime_open(mode) {\nconsole.log('kaime_open mode: %s', mode);\nif ('open' == mode) {\ncur_mode = 'open';\n} else {\ncur_mode = 'close';\n}\n}\n//------------------------------------------------------------\nfunction check_mark() {\nconsole.log('check_mark');\nvar ret = false;\nfor (var key in cur_mark) {\nvar val = key.split('-');\nif (1 == val[0]) {\nret = true;\n}\n}\nreturn ret;\n}\n//------------------------------------------------------------\n// 印 ◎:1 単一選択\n//\t   ○:2 単一選択\n//\t   ▲:3 単一選択\n//\t   △:4 複数選択\n//------------------------------------------------------------\nfunction initial_animate_mark() {\nconsole.log('initial_animate_mark');\ncur_mark = {};\nfor (var i = 1; i <= 4; i++) {\n$('input[type=radio][id^=m' + i + '-]').each(function() {\nvar id = $(this).prop('id').replace(/^m/, '');\nvar val = id.split('-');\nvar radio = sprintf(\"m%s-%s\", val[0], val[1]);\nvar label = sprintf(\"ml%s-%s\", val[0], val[1]);\n$('#' + radio).prop('checked', false);\n$('#' + label).removeClass('Selected');\n});\n}\n}\nfunction animate_mark(p_seq, p_m) {\n//\t console.log('animate_mark(%s,%s)', p_seq, p_m);\n// 's': single select 'm': multi select\nvar mark_type = {\n1: 's',\n2: 's',\n3: 's',\n4: 'm'\n};\nvar cur_id = sprintf(\"%s-%s\", p_m, p_seq);\nvar cur_radio = sprintf(\"m%s-%s\", p_m, p_seq);\nvar cur_label = sprintf(\"ml%s-%s\", p_m, p_seq);\nfor (var i = 1; i <= 4; i++) {\nif (i == p_m) {\ncontinue;\n}\n$('input[type=radio][id^=m' + i + '-]').each(function() {\nvar id = $(this).prop('id').replace(/^m/, '');\nvar val = id.split('-');\nvar radio = sprintf(\"m%s-%s\", val[0], val[1]);\nvar label = sprintf(\"ml%s-%s\", val[0], val[1]);\nif (val[1] == p_seq) {\ndelete cur_mark[id];\n$('#' + radio).prop('checked', false);\n$('#' + label).removeClass('Selected');\n//\t\t\t\t console.log('id: %s checked <- false',id);\n}\n});\n}\nif (cur_mark[cur_id]) {\ndelete cur_mark[cur_id];\n$('#' + cur_radio).prop('checked', false);\n$('#' + cur_label).removeClass('Selected');\n//\t\t\t console.log('cur_id: %s checked <- false',cur_id);\n} else {\ncur_mark[cur_id] = true;\n$('#' + cur_radio).prop('checked', true);\n$('#' + cur_label).addClass('Selected');\n//\t\t\t console.log('cur_id: %s cur_radio: %s cur_label: %s',cur_id,cur_radio,cur_label);\n}\nif ('s' == mark_type[p_m]) {\n$('input[type=radio][id^=m' + p_m + '-]').each(function() {\nvar id = $(this).prop('id').replace(/^m/, '');\nvar val = id.split('-');\nvar radio = sprintf(\"m%s-%s\", val[0], val[1]);\nvar label = sprintf(\"ml%s-%s\", val[0], val[1]);\nif (id != cur_id) {\ndelete cur_mark[id];\n$('#' + radio).prop('checked', false);\n$('#' + label).removeClass('Selected');\n//\t\t\t\t console.log('id: %s checked <- false',id);\n}\n});\n}\n}\n/*\n* 確認ダイアログ(カスタム)\n*/\nfunction ConfirmDialog(title, message, fn) {\nconsole.log('ConfirmDialog');\n$.confirm({\nuseBootstrap: false,\nboxWidth: '70%',\ntitle: title,\ncontent: message,\ncolumnClass: 'small',\n//\t     theme: 'modern',\ntheme: 'material',\ntype: 'orange',\ntypeAnimated: true,\nbuttons: {\nyes: {\ntext: 'はい',\nbtnClass: 'btn-orange',\naction: function() {\nif(undefined !== fn){\nfn(true);\n}\n}\n},\nno: {\ntext: 'いいえ',\nbtnClass: 'btn-default',\naction: function() {\nif(undefined !== fn){\nfn(false);\n}\n}\n},\n}\n});\n}\nfunction AlertDialog(title, message, fn) {\nconsole.log('NoticeDialog');\n$.alert({\nuseBootstrap: false,\nboxWidth: '70%',\ntitle: title,\ncontent: message,\ncolumnClass: 'small',\ntheme: 'material',\ntype: 'orange',\ntypeAnimated: true,\nbuttons: {\nyes: {\ntext: '確認',\nbtnClass: 'btn-orange',\naction: function() {\nif(undefined !== fn){\nfn(true);\n}\n}\n},\n}\n});\n}\n// 俺プロ会員登録＆完了画面表示\nfunction do_regist_member( fn ){\nvar _data = {};\n_data.input  = 'UTF-8';\n_data.output = 'jsonp';\n$.ajax({\ntype: \"GET\",\nurl: \"https://orepro.netkeiba.com/api/api_regist_orepro_member.html\",\ndata: _data,\ndataType : 'jsonp',\nsuccess: function(json){\nif(json.status == 'OK'){\nif(undefined !== fn){\nconsole.log('callback');\nfn();\n}\n}\n},\nerror: function(XMLHttpRequest, textStatus, errorThrown) {\nconsole.error('通信に失敗しました。\\n恐れいりますが、時間をおいて再度お試し下さい。'); // エラー表示\n}\n});\n}\n// ログイン前状態で投票ボタン押下時の案内ダイアログ\nfunction regist_pop_open(){\n$('body').append('<div id=\"Overflow_Bg\"></div>').css({'height':'100vh','overflow':'hidden'});\n$('#Regist_Pop').fadeIn('fast');\n$(window).on('touchmove.noScroll', function(e) {\ne.preventDefault();\n});\n}\nfunction regist_pop_close(){\n$('body').css({'height':'auto','overflow':'auto'});\n$('#Regist_Pop').fadeOut('fast');\n$('#Overflow_Bg').remove();\n$(window).off('.noScroll');\n}\n//------------------------------------------------------------\n// 投票モード切替処理(簡単or買い目)\nfunction change_simple_bet_mode( mode, db_save, scroll_top ){\nconsole.log(\"change_simple_bet_mode[mode=\"+mode+\",db_save=\"+db_save+\"]\");\nif( mode == 'on' ){// 簡単モード\n$('.ModeToggleBlock').hide();\nvar _param = { simple_bet : 'y' };\n}else if( mode == 'off' ){// 買い目モード\n$('.ModeToggleBlock').show();\nvar _param = { simple_bet : 'n' };\n}\nif( db_save == true ){\nif(undefined != _param){\napi_user_setting(url_user_setting, 'set', _param, function(data) {\nconsole.log('data: %O', data);\nconsole.log('db save success!');\n// DBを更新\nif( scroll_top == true ){\n$(window).scrollTop( 0 );// 切替直後に画面上部に移動\n}\n});\n}\n}else{\n// DBを更新しない\nif( scroll_top == true ){\n$(window).scrollTop( 0 );// 切替直後に画面上部に移動\n}\n}\n}\n});\n});\n});\n});\n});\n});\n});\n// 現在のURLを記録してnetkeibaに遷移\nvar _cart_group_premium = 'premium';\nvar _regist_url = 'https://regist.netkeiba.com/account/?pid=user_add';\nvar _return_url = 'https://orepro.netkeiba.com/bet/shutuba.html?race_id=202606030302&mode=init';\n$('#Regist_Action').on('click',function(){\njQuery.getScript(\"https://cdn.netkeiba.com/img.orepro//common/js/social_cart.js?2015090301\", function(){\nvar ary_item_id = ['return_url'];\nvar ary_val = [0];\nvar ary_price = [0];\nvar ary_cdata = [ _return_url ];\ncart_clear_item( _cart_group_premium, function(){\ncart_add_item( _cart_group_premium, ary_item_id, ary_val, ary_price, ary_cdata, cb_regist_location );\n});\nfunction cb_regist_location( json ){\nconsole.log('cb_regist_location(%O)',json);\nwindow.location.href = _regist_url;\n}\n});\n});\n//制作追記　テキストエリアリサイズ\nfunction resize_textarea(ev) {\n//if (ev.keyCode != 13) return;\nvar textarea = ev.target || ev.srcElement;\nvar value = textarea.value;\nvar lines = 1;\nfor (var i = 0, l = value.length; i < l; i++) {\nif (value.charAt(i) == '\\n') lines++;\n}\ntextarea.setAttribute(\"rows\", lines);\n}\n</script>\n<!-- ↓カスタムダイアログ(alert,confirm) -->\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdn.netkeiba.com/img.orepro//common/css/sweetalert_orepro_custom.min.css?20190410b\" media=\"screen\">\n<script src=\"https://cdn.netkeiba.com/img.sp/common/js/sweetalert.min.js\" async></script>\n<!-- ↑カスタムダイアログ(alert,confirm) -->\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- /. Contents -->\n</div>\n<!-- block=netkeiba_footer_pc (d) -->\n<footer>\n<div class=\"NkFooterArea\">\n<div class=\"BtnPagetop\">\n<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\"ページトップへ\"></a>\n</div><!-- /.BtnPagetop -->\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\n$(function() {\n$('.BtnPagetop a').click(function () {\n$('body,html').animate({\nscrollTop: 0\n}, 400);\nreturn false;\n});\n});\n</script>\n<div class=\"KeirinLink01\">\n<a href=\"//keirin.netkeiba.com/?rf=nk_pc_footer\" title=\"netkeirin\"><img src=\"https://cdn.netkeiba.com/img.www/style/netkeiba.ja/image/common/PC_footer_bnr01.png\" alt=\"いま競輪が熱い！nerkeirinで競輪を気軽に楽しもう\" /></a>\n</div><!-- /.KeirinLink01 -->\n<dl class=\"FootSiteTitle fc\">\n<dt>\n<a href=\"https://www.netkeiba.com?rf=footer\" title=\"netkeiba\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.netkeiba.com/img.www/style/netkeiba.ja/image/common/netkeiba_logo01.png\" alt=\"netkeiba\" />\n</a>\n</dt>\n<dd>\n<p>利用者数<strong>1700</strong>万人突破！<strong>No.1</strong>競馬サイト</p>\n</dd>\n</dl>\n<div class=\"FootWrap\">\n<dl class=\"NkFoot01 NkFootCateLink\">\n<dt>カテゴリ</dt>\n<dd class=\"fc\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://news.netkeiba.com?rf=footer\" title=\"ニュース\">ニュース</a>\n</li>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://race.netkeiba.com/top/?rf=footer\" title=\"レース\">レース</a>\n</li>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://yoso.netkeiba.com?rf=footer\" title=\"ウマい馬券\">ウマい馬券</a>\n</li>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://news.netkeiba.com?pid=column_top&rf=footer\" title=\"コラム\">コラム</a>\n</li>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://tv.netkeiba.com?rf=footer\" title=\"netkeibaTV\">netkeibaTV</a>\n</li>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://nar.netkeiba.com/top/?rf=footer\" title=\"地方競馬\">地方競馬</a>\n</li>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://db.netkeiba.com?rf=footer\" title=\"データベース\">データベース</a>\n</li>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://orepro.netkeiba.com?rf=footer\" title=\"俺プロ\">俺プロ</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://owner.netkeiba.com?rf=footer\" title=\"一口馬主\">一口馬主</a>\n</li>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://pog.netkeiba.com?rf=footer\" title=\"POG\">POG</a>\n</li>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://bbs.pc.keiba.findfriends.jp?rf=footer\" title=\"競馬広場\">競馬広場</a>\n</li>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://dir.netkeiba.com/keibamatome/index.html?rf=footer\" title=\"まとめ\">まとめ</a>\n</li>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://yoso.netkeiba.com/senmonshi/?rf=footer\" title=\"競馬新聞\">競馬新聞</a>\n</li>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://race.netkeiba.com/bookmark/bookmark.html?rf=footer\" title=\"お気に入り馬\">お気に入り馬</a>\n</li>\n<li>\n<a h